  "local_port": 36652,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the jobs one can do from home?",
  "response": "Working from home has become increasingly popular, offering flexibility and the ability to balance personal and professional life. Here are various jobs one can do from home across different fields:\n\n### **1. Writing and Content Creation**\n- **Freelance Writer**  \n- **Content Creator**  \n- **Blogger**  \n- **Copywriter**  \n- **Technical Writer**  \n- **Editor/Proofreader**  \n- **Ghostwriter**  \n- **Scriptwriter**  \n\n---\n\n### **2. Design and Creative Arts**\n- **Graphic Designer**  \n- **Web Designer**  \n- **Illustrator**  \n- **Photographer (Editing)**  \n- **Video Editor**  \n- **Animator**  \n- **Interior Designer (Virtual)**  \n- **UI/UX Designer**  \n\n---\n\n### **3. Technology and IT**\n- **Software Developer**  \n- **Web Developer**  \n- **App Developer**  \n- **Data Analyst**  \n- **Cybersecurity Specialist**  \n- **IT Support Specialist**  \n- **Cloud Engineer**  \n- **AI/Machine Learning Specialist**  \n\n---\n\n### **4. Marketing and Social Media**\n- **Social Media Manager**  \n- **Digital Marketing Specialist**  \n- **SEO Specialist**  \n- **Email Marketing Manager**  \n- **Content Strategist**  \n- **Influencer Marketing Specialist**  \n- **Affiliate Marketer**  \n\n---\n\n### **5. Customer Service and Administration**\n- **Virtual Assistant**  \n- **Customer Support Representative**  \n- **Call Center Agent**  \n- **Data Entry Specialist**  \n- **Scheduler/Appointment Setter**  \n- **Transcriptionist**  \n- **Online Chat Support**  \n\n---\n\n### **6. Education and Training**\n- **Online Tutor**  \n- **Instructional Designer**  \n- **E-learning Developer**  \n- **Curriculum Developer**  \n- **Language Instructor**  \n- **Test Prep Coach**  \n- **Virtual Trainer**  \n\n---\n\n### **7. Sales and Consulting**\n- **Sales Representative**  \n- **Business Consultant**  \n- **Life Coach**  \n- **Career Coach**  \n- **Financial Advisor**  \n- **Real Estate Agent (Virtual)**  \n- **E-commerce Consultant**  \n\n---\n\n### **8. Healthcare and Wellness**\n- **Telehealth Nurse**  \n- **Medical Coder/Biller**  \n- **Counselor/Therapist (Online)**  \n- **Health Coach**  \n- **Nutritionist/Dietitian (Virtual)**  \n- **Yoga Instructor (Online)**  \n- **Fitness Trainer (Online)**  \n\n---\n\n### **9. Accounting and Finance**\n- **Bookkeeper**  \n- **Accountant**  \n- **Tax Preparer**  \n- **Financial Analyst**  \n- **Payroll Specialist**  \n- **Auditor (Remote)**  \n\n---\n\n### **10. E-commerce and Entrepreneurship**\n- **E-commerce Store Owner**  \n- **Dropshipping Business Owner**  \n- **Print-on-Demand Business**  \n- **Freelance Entrepreneur**  \n- **Digital Product Creator**  \n- **Affiliate Marketing Business**  \n\n---\n\n### **11. Legal and Administrative**\n- **Paralegal (Remote)**  \n- **Legal Transcriptionist**  \n- **Virtual Receptionist**  \n- **Administrative Support Specialist**  \n\n---\n\n### **12. Translating and Language Services**\n- **Translator**  \n- **Interpreter (Remote)**  \n- **Language Tutor**  \n- **Localization Specialist**  \n\n---\n\n### **13. Gaming and Entertainment**\n- **Game Developer**  \n- **Streamer/YouTuber**  \n- **Esports Player/Coach**  \n- **Game Tester**  \n\n---\n\n### **14. Research and Analysis**\n- **Market Researcher**  \n- **Academic Researcher**  \n- **Data Researcher**  \n- **Business Analyst**  \n\n---\n\n### **15. Miscellaneous**\n- **Online Moderator**  \n- **Proofreader**  \n- **Voiceover Artist**  \n- **Podcast Producer**  \n- **Event Planner (Virtual)**  \n\nThese roles often require specific skills, tools, and sometimes certifications. Platforms like Upwork, Fiverr, LinkedIn, and remote-specific job boards can help find opportunities tailored to your expertise.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
